-- B y   I l y a   K h r e n n i k o v
-- 2012-08-27T04:20:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-27/russian-intelligence-service-to-monitor-blogs-kommersant-says.html
Russia’s Foreign Intelligence
Service will pay about $1 million to develop systems for
“monitoring the blogosphere” and “shaping the public opinion
via social networks”,  Kommersant , said without citing anyone.  To contact the reporter on this story:
